Manjaro KDE 裝完nvidia driver 會有tearing問題，上網碌嘢同睇片嗰陣最難頂<img src="/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif" class="hkgmoji" /> <img src="/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif" class="hkgmoji" /> <img src="/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif" class="hkgmoji" /> <br />
<br />
要加下面Option嗰堆嘢至冇事<img src="/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif" class="hkgmoji" /> <br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type=""># kate /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/20-nvidia.conf

Section &quot;Screen&quot;
    Option         &quot;metamodes&quot; &quot;nvidia-auto-select +0+0 {ForceCompositionPipeline=On, ForceFullCompositionPipeline=Off}&quot;
    Option         &quot;AllowIndirectGLXProtocol&quot; &quot;off&quot;
    Option         &quot;TripleBuffer&quot; &quot;on&quot;</code></pre>
